data.description: $10,000 seller credit and a motivated seller looking to sell fast is a great opportunity for you to become a new homeowner! Behold this remarkable 5-bedroom, 4-bath farmhouse set on a sprawling 1.8-acre lot! Boasting nearly 4000 square feet of living space, the original garage has been transformed into a magnificent bedroom, creating a potential second master bedroom.  The living areas are equally impressive, featuring a family room with whitewashed beams, an elegant formal dining room, and a sunroom flooding with natural light. The kitchen is a showstopper with concrete glazed countertops, a sparkling black finish, a brick backsplash, and high-end stainless-steel appliances. A breakfast nook leads to a screened-in porch and a wrap-around deck with panoramic views.  Upstairs, the master bedroom offers a spacious walk-in closet and access to an unfinished attic, perfect for a children's play area or bonus room. Two additional bedrooms share a well-appointed hall bathroom. Beyond the beauty, the current owner invested over $100k in a concrete driveway, a detached 2-car garage, and a workshop, ideal for a gym or studio. No HOA means you can have your own chickens.  Situated in a community with a shared well system, this genuine treasure is just a short 15-minute drive from Simpsonville or downtown Greenville. Seize this incredible opportunity to own your own piece of paradise!
